  "body": "IMO it's surprising that `kubectl delete foo --force` does not force delete a resource. `--force` only takes effect when `--grace-period=0`. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/7bcfbcd58515421d9756fc9bf89371c4e5257b2b/pkg/kubectl/cmd/delete.go#L211-L221\r\n\r\nThe description of `--force` reads this: `Immediate deletion of some resources may result in inconsistency or data loss and requires confirmation.`\r\n\r\nWe should make it more clear what `--force` does and even print warnings when `--force` is specified without `--grace-period=0`. \r\n\r\n@kubernetes/sig-cli-maintainers @smarterclayton ",
